TEXT.TITLE: COLLINS FOODS <CF> TO REDEEM DEBENTURES
TEXT.BODY: Collins Foods International Inc said that on April 30 it will redeem all of its outstanding 12 pct subordinated debentures due December 15, 2008. There are currently 30 mln dlrs principal amount of the debentures outstanding, the company said. Reuter
